songs.title: Rock Your Candies
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: Ally & Dinah]
Beep, beep, cruise, the boys in the ride
Had to stop them, don't want just them walking by
Got me feeling so right
I can stay up all night

[Verse 2: Lauren & Normani]
Looking sweet, sweet in my Candies today
And there's nobody keeping up with my shoe game
Now I'm calling all my girls
Getting ready for the turn up, sing it, Fifth Harmony

[Chorus: All & Camila]
All my ladies stand up, all my ladies stand up
Rock your candies
All my ladies stand up, all my ladies stand up
In your candies
All my ladies stand up, all my ladies stand up
And rock your candies
All my ladies stand up, all my ladies stand up
In your candies

[Verse 1: Dinah & Lauren]
If I like it then I gotta get another
Your girls got it in every colour
Got the dress, purse, craft skirts
Got the whole crew on fleek

[Verse 2: Normani & Ally]
I keep the new, cute tops, tight jeans
But I'm a Candies pump girl low key
If I tell you that I'm shopping
You know where to come find me

[Chorus: All & Camila]
All my ladies stand up, all my ladies stand up
Rock your candies
All my ladies stand up, all my ladies stand up
In your candies
All my ladies stand up, all my ladies stand up
And rock your candies
All my ladies stand up, all my ladies stand up
In your candies
